because they saw,

00:34:43.699 --> 00:34:46.370
they heard something in
Spotify, or Google, or whatever,

00:34:46.370 --> 00:34:47.210
YouTube.

00:34:47.210 --> 00:34:49.580
And they went oh, why,
I really, really liked

00:34:49.580 --> 00:34:51.350
that person's work.

00:34:51.350 --> 00:34:53.719
I'm going to try and
book her, and maybe you

00:34:53.719 --> 00:34:55.520
do it right from the song.

00:34:55.520 --> 00:34:57.950
And you link, or you say,
I love that trumpet player.

00:34:57.950 --> 00:34:59.550
I want to put that
trumpet player--

00:34:59.550 --> 00:35:01.640
I want to put that
trumpet in my film,

00:35:01.640 --> 00:35:04.730
and then they put
the trumpet player.

00:35:04.730 --> 00:35:07.520
But if we don't have a
way to kind of go, here

00:35:07.520 --> 00:35:11.090
I am, and here are my songs,
we don't have anything

00:35:11.090 --> 00:35:11.780
to build from.

00:35:11.780 --> 00:35:13.820
We don't have a home.

00:35:13.820 --> 00:35:17.810
BEN ARTHUR: Imagine you were
