I think-- we're not ready
for big integration yet.

00:35:36.980 --> 00:35:41.000
We need to go kind of and create
a groundswell among musicians

00:35:41.000 --> 00:35:45.110
so they kind of own this space
because this is an autonomous

00:35:45.110 --> 00:35:47.060
thing we need to do.

00:35:47.060 --> 00:35:51.680
We need to convince music makers
to take charge of their data

00:35:51.680 --> 00:35:55.880
