00:37:37.660 --> 00:37:39.710
You know, and that's
their incentive.

00:37:39.710 --> 00:37:44.150
But for us, it's
how can we create

00:37:44.150 --> 00:37:48.260
a beautiful, healthy,
living kind of ecosystem

00:37:48.260 --> 00:37:52.400
from which these services
can grow kind of on our--

00:37:52.400 --> 00:37:53.660
that makes sense for us.

00:37:53.660 --> 00:37:55.140
And then we're
truly sustainable,

00:37:55.140 --> 00:37:59.420
and then we can have centuries
