become this big Alexandria.

00:41:27.600 --> 00:41:28.530
Who knows?

00:41:28.530 --> 00:41:30.320
If we can kind of make--

00:41:30.320 --> 00:41:32.070
if we can find a way
in for the musicians,

00:41:32.070 --> 00:41:34.830
and it can grow
further, otherwise it

00:41:34.830 --> 00:41:38.880
will just became become
another kind of clearinghouse,

00:41:38.880 --> 00:41:41.880
kind of closed space, which
will have all this money put

00:41:41.880 --> 00:41:46.880
into it by the public money, but
it won't be further reaching.

00:41:46.880 --> 00:41:48.818
It will just be another
closed database,

00:41:48.818 --> 00:41:49.860
and that will be a shame.

